{"tid":831061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"追女仔","createTime":"2018-09-21T15:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T16:42:43.000Z","uid":198526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c870fd71927d43639bff9bdea1029675786e6114","tid":831061,"uid":198526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我最近返學識左個女仔 關係都幾CLOSE 上堂都2個坐， 之後有個男性朋友就睇到我對條女有意思 就話 一場兄弟 製造D機會幫下你。<br />\n<br />\n之後我一開始就信佢係想幫我啦，點知比我FEEL到佢係想自己溝條女。<br />\n佢之前講到出口話 唔溝 咁我先信任佢 點知而家好似中左佢計一樣 各位巴絲點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求各位可以醒我幾招 還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">利申:條仔樣衰 但勝在好無賴 唔知醜<br />\n         我就正正常常文青樣(方大同之類) </span><br />\n<br />\n隨便屌我 希望百屌成材 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a428350b814307bfa6778993911a3e6163f7ab7","tid":831061,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"文青樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直接講弱智樣咪得囉"},{"pid":"abda341499267a16573c72e8b7f9244de55c2fac","tid":831061,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"似方大同咁樣衰都好意思話自己正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4812f834c486b115bd6cf12a7ab06de7ac26918","tid":831061,"uid":180073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"你有人地聯絡方式未？<br />\n你約過人出街？<br />\n拖咗手？<br />\n抱過？<br />\nKISS？<br />\n你咩都唔做   叫人點幫你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p